IMAGES FOLDER — Drop your images here
======================================

Just put your image files in this folder and they will show up automatically.
No need to edit the HTML — just use the exact filenames listed below:

  profile.jpg       → Your photo (shown on the About page)
  project-01.jpg    → Convenience Inventory System screenshot
  project-02.jpg    → Recipe Masters screenshot
  project-03.jpg    → Restack screenshot

Supported formats: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .webp
(If you use a different format, update the src= in the HTML to match.)

Place: portfolio/images/your-image.jpg
